::: {.cell layout-align="center"}

```{.r .cell-code}
plot(x = mtcars$wt, y = mtcars$mpg, 
     main = "MPG vs. Weight", 
     xlab = "Car Weight", 
     ylab = "Miles Per Gallon", 
     pch = 16, col = 4, las = 1)
```

